# What do the peripherals need to do?
- shall receive voice input from user, transmit to PU, 
- lcd shall give clear, easy to read messages to the user, making sure they know what to do
- board must fit the corexy and other components inside of it
- pieces must be sized according to the board and the magnet being used to move them

# How do we do that?
microphone communicating via USB to arduino
i2c lcd screen


